"""
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║   NSE STOCK / INDEX FUTURES  ·  Pure Price Action                    ║
║   N-Bar Donchian Channel Breakout  ·  ZERO INDICATORS               ║
║   8-Year Daily Backtest  ·  Full NSE Charges  ·  Monte Carlo         ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

WHY THIS APPROACH:
  • Donchian Channel = raw OHLCV only (N-bar highest high / lowest low)
  • Zero computed indicators — no moving averages, no std dev, nothing
  • 8 years of daily data → statistically robust, covers multiple regimes
  • Price-based stops (channel extremes), not arbitrary % levels
  • R-multiple take profit (risk-defined reward)
"""

